id: pm-ne67
title: Add --compact mode to pm activity for agent-friendly condensed output
description: "pm activity output embeds full JSON-patch arrays per operation, making it very verbose. Agents scanning for recent changes have to parse ~100-line patch blocks. A --compact mode showing only op, id, ts, author per entry would reduce output by ~90% for common audit workflows."
type: Feature
status: open
priority: 2
tags[4]: activity,agents,output,ux
